<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Jamie's Chess</title>
    <link href="/css/main.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="/css/index.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
</head>
<body>
<header>
    Jamie's Chess Game
</header>
<section>
    <div class="blank">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="room">
        <label class="mini-title">체스 게임을 시작하시겠습니까?</label><br/>
        <br/>
        <form action="/room/{roomId}/game/{gameId}" id="form-game" method="get">
        </form>
        <label class="room-name">화이트팀 이름(기본 WHITE) : </label>
        <input class="room-combo" id="white-name" maxlength="10" name="whiteName" type="text"/><br>
        <label class="room-name">블랙팀 이름(기본 BLACK) : </label>
        <input class="room-combo" id="black-name" maxlength="10" name="blackName" type="text"/><br>
        <button class="room-button" id="start-button">게임 시작하기</button>
        <button class="room-button" id="load-button">게임 이어하기</button>
        <br/>
        <br/>
        <label class="red-label">* 게임 이어하기시, 이어할 게임이 없으면 위의 이름들로 새 게임을 진행합니다.</label>
    </div>
    <div class="blank">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="room">
        <label class="mini-title">그 동안의 결과를 확인하세요.</label><br/>
        <br/>
        <form action="/result" id="result-game" method="get">
            <button class="room-button" id="result-button">게임 결과보기</button>
        </form>
    </div>
    <div class="blank">&nbsp;</div>
    <div class="room">
        <label class="mini-title">다시 방을 선택 하시겠습니까?</label><br/>
        <br/>
        <button class="room-button" id="room-button">방 선택</button>
    </div>
</section>
<script src="/js/room.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
</body>
</html>